From the main Sass map we then create shortcut variables for each type size, as well as a set of memorable alias variables e.g. `-xxs`, `-xs`, `-sm`, `-md`, `-lg`, `-xl`, `-xxl`.

{{< code lang="scss" >}}// Type Size variables

